---
/** * THE LINEAR PIPELINE: HOW IT WORKS
 * Consistency: Studio White, Plus Jakarta Sans, Hand-drawn Accents
 * Style: Interconnected Flow, KES/Kenya Focused
 */
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="relative py-24 lg:py-40 bg-white overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#030A8C 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,#030A8C/2_0%,transparent_70%)] opacity-30"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-24">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 mb-8">
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#F29F05]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
        </svg>
        <span class="text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#030A8C]">The 3-Step Transformation</span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-[#0D0D0D] tracking-tight leading-[0.95] mb-6">
        Ready in <span class="text-[#030A8C]">Minutes.</span><br/>
        Built for <span class="text-[#F29F05]">Scale.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Transition from legacy paperwork to AI-driven HR excellence faster than your morning coffee.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-[10%] right-[10%] h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#030A8C]/20 via-[#F29F05]/30 to-[#030A8C]/20 z-0"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 text-center group">
        <div class="relative h-24 w-24 rounded-[32px] bg-white border-4 border-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 group-hover:shadow-[#030A8C]/20 group-hover:-translate-y-2">
          <span class="text-3xl font-black text-[#030A8C]">01</span>
          <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-4 h-4 bg-[#F29F05] rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#0D0D0D] mb-4 tracking-tighter">Onboard & Configure</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
          Create your profile and map your Kenyan tax requirements (KRA, NHIF, NSSF) using our guided AI setup wizard.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 text-center group">
        <div class="relative h-24 w-24 rounded-[32px] bg-[#030A8C] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 shadow-2xl shadow-[#030A8C]/40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110">
          <span class="text-3xl font-black text-white">02</span>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-[32px] bg-[#030A8C] animate-ping opacity-20"></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#0D0D0D] mb-4 tracking-tighter">AI-Sync Data</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
          Upload your existing CSV or Excel sheets. Our AI automatically cleans data, identifies errors, and categorizes staff.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 text-center group">
        <div class="relative h-24 w-24 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:rotate-6">
           <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full text-[#F29F05] opacity-90 scale-125" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" preserveAspectRatio="none">
             <path d="M5,50 C5,10 95,10 95,50 C95,90 5,90 7,55" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
           </svg>
           <span class="text-3xl font-black text-[#0D0D0D] relative z-10">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#0D0D0D] mb-4 tracking-tighter">Automate & Scale</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
          Activate bulk M-Pesa payouts, automated performance tracking, and real-time KES outflow reporting.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto p-1 bg-[#F8FAFC] rounded-[40px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
       <div class="bg-white rounded-[36px] p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
             <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#F29F05]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#F29F05]">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                   <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                </svg>
             </div>
             <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-[#030A8C] uppercase tracking-widest">Active Setup Wizard</p>
                <p class="text-lg font-black text-[#0D0D0D]">Onboarding Progress: 85%</p>
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-64 h-3 bg-gray-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
             <div class="h-full bg-[#030A8C] w-[85%] animate-pulse"></div>
          </div>
          <button class="bg-[#0D0D0D] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-black text-sm hover:bg-[#030A8C] transition-all">
             Continue Setup
          </button>
       </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;700;800&display=swap');

  section {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  h2 {
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
</style>